Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:12.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（藍原延珠(あいはらえんじゅ)）\N蓮太郎(れんたろう) 自衛隊 勝つかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.99,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro... Do you think the JASDF will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（里見(さとみ)蓮太郎）分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:18.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（戦闘音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.49,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,The fighting stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:22.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（片桐(かたぎり)玉樹(たまき)）戦闘がやんだぞ\N勝ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.12,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,Did we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:27.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎･延珠）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:33.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（人々の悲鳴）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:40.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:44.29,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Th-Th-That's... impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:44.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな バカな！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:51.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:14.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:19.10,Bullet_Ep_Title,ep 11,0,0,0,,{\fad(465,460)}#11 The Heart of Taurus, The Spear of Light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（我堂(がどう)英彦(ひでひこ)）\N総員 戦闘用意！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.67,Bullet_Main,hide,0,0,0,,{\a6}All hands prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ティナ）お兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.13,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:25.72,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別動隊か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,A detachment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も気づいてねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.11,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,No one else saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:36.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,挟み撃ちにされたら\N俺たち全滅だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:36.63,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,If they flank us, we're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（薙沢彰磨(なぎさわしょうま)）\Nだが 勝手に陣を離れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.84,Bullet_Main,shou,0,0,0,,However, leaving the camp would be a clear violation of our orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明確な命令違反だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？ 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:42.88,Bullet_Main,shou,0,0,0,,What do you want to do, Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（片桐弓月(ゆづき)）あんたが決めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.64,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,You decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしたちは\Nリーダーの言うことを聞くから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.64,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,We'll listen to our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.40,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（英彦）里見リーダー？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.65,Bullet_Main,hide,0,0,0,,Leader Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこへ行く！\N列に戻れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.55,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you going? \NReturn to your position!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガストレアの雄たけび）\N（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）マズい！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:18.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（天童(てんどう)木更(きさら)）任せて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:19.80,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:24.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童式抜刀術 一の型八番
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.18,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Tendo Martial Arts Sword Drawing \NFirst Style, Number 8:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無影無踪(むえいむそう)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.97,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Muei Muso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒュ～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,木更さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:34.31,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Kisara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:41.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（布施(ふせ) 翠(みどり)）里見リーダー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.07,Bullet_Main,fuse,0,0,0,,Leader Satomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わりました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.45,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,we've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）強い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.01,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,We're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.58,Bullet_Italics,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 急いで戻るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All right! Let's hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:00.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:03.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガストレアの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:09.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.60,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.50,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,At this rate, we're all done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ 全滅だ\Nあっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:17.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなは ここで援護を頼む！\N（木更）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.98,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All of you, stay here and back me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:19.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.00,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:24.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた 今すぐ 撤退の指示を出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.95,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry and tell everyone to fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（英彦）やあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:25.97,Bullet_Main,hide,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見リーダーじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.28,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,if it isn't Leader Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は 光の槍(やり)を見たかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.96,Bullet_Main,hide,0,0,0,,Have you seen the Spear of Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光の槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Spear of Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんなものがあるんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.46,Bullet_Main,hide,0,0,0,,With that thing on their side,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:43.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らには 最初から\N勝ち目はなかったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:43.88,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,we never stood a chance from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.39,Bullet_Main,hide,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心音(ここね)だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.24,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,This is Kokone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後まで 一緒にいようって\Nずっと 手を握り合っていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.75,Bullet_Main,hide,0,0,0,,We were holding hands the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.90,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,saying we'd be together until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこを光の槍に襲われた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.76,Bullet_Main,hide,0,0,0,,And then the Spear of Light attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:03.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フハハハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）光の槍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.64,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The Spear of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警たち）うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:43.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アルデバランの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバラン…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Alde... baran...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:47.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（民警）おい 見ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.91,Bullet_Main,civil,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアが引いていくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.40,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,The Gastrea are falling back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉樹）ひでえもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.67,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,Man, this is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 何人 死んだんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.37,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,Just how many people died?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）たぶん 半数は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.92,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Probably about half...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵だって だいぶ減っただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.41,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,The enemy forces have \Nalso dwindled, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:13.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 減った分だけ増えている\N（玉樹）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,But whatever they lost, they gained back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:13.39,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,民警 自衛隊含め
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:17.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Including both civil officers and JASDF,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000人以上は\Nガストレア化しただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.65,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,over a thousand have turned into Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉樹）ってことは\Nガストレア2000体に対して―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:24.59,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,Meaning... there's only 500 \Nof us against 2,000 of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは500人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:27.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）絶望的な数字だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It's a despairing number...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.13,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！ イヒヒッ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.71,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ どうしたんだ？ それ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.84,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かわいいだろう\N手伝ってたら くれたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.86,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.59,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,They gave it to me because I was helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふーん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.18,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪魔になってたんじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.50,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,You sure you weren't in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.53,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:07:01.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケガ人の手を握ってあげて\Nすごくいいって評判になってるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.33,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,She holds the hands of the wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.65,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,They all say she's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へえー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾(わらわ) 役に立ってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.57,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I am being useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:07.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はいはい\Nすげえよ お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.90,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're amazing, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（室戸(むろと) 菫(すみれ)）こんばんは 蓮太郎くん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.63,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,Good evening, Rentaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.95,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful night, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい夜だね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:16.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生　どうして こんな所に？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:16.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Sensei, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここを統括するように\N要請があってね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:19.54,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,I was asked to supervise things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:22.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた 確か シェルターの抽選に\N当たってたよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:23.12,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You won a spot in the shelter, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:25.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たったんじゃなくて\Nもらったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.78,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,I didn't win it; they gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:29.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日本最高の頭脳に死なれたら\N困るってね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:29.55,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,They said they couldn't allow the \Ngreatest brain in Japan to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その場で 破り捨てたがね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.40,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,Though, I ripped it up on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨てるぐらいなら 誰かにやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You could've given it to someone if you \Nwere just going to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:36.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菫）誰に？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.02,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,To who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,砂漠にコップ１杯の水が\Nあっても―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.41,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,If there were only a cup \Nof water in the desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを巡って\N殺し合いが始まるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:42.56,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,they'd just kill each other to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の東京エリアで―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.00,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,I can't imagine we'd find
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全員の喉を潤せるようなオアシスが\N見つかるとは思えない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:49.19,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,an oasis in the Tokyo Area that \Ncould quench everyone's thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私がここに来たのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.32,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,The reason I'm here is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この砂漠を抜けようと\Nもくろんだバカどもを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.91,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,because I wanted to cheer on \Nthe idiots who are trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,応援してやりたくなったからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.08,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,get out of the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生は もっと論理的な人間だと\N思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I thought you were a much \Nmore logical person, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:06.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間は 論理でものを考え\N感情で動くんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.03,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,Humans tend to think logically,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.03,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,but their actions are driven by emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行動したまえ 蓮太郎くん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.45,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,Take action, Rentaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:12.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち止まれば 死に追いつかれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:12.34,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,If you stop, death will catch up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:14.74,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがと 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.79,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと 延珠のことだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:20.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Also, about Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:24.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラスメートが亡くなった話なら\N聞いている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.33,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,If it's about her losing her \Nclassmates, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,災難だったね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.33,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,That was quite the tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生 医者から見て\N延珠はどうなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Sensei, from a doctor's \Nperspective, how's Enju doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:35.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心したまえ\Nたぶん もう大丈夫だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.26,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I think she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠ちゃんのメンタルは―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:40.74,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,Enju-chan's mental stability \Nis far stronger than we imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちが思っているより\Nずっと強い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.18,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うたぐり深い男だねえ 君も
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.56,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,You're a very skeptical man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:49.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ 念のために事件のことを\N思い出させるような言動は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.49,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,Well, I'd avoid bringing up \Nanything that would remind her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.28,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,of the incident, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慎みたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 君たちは\Nもう 帰って休みたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.72,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,You two should go back and rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更･延珠）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）やだ なんか不気味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.51,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Ugh, this place is sort of creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）\Nここがそうなのか？ 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.90,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Is this the place, Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:10.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）彰磨兄(にい)の話だと\Nそのはずなんだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:10.77,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,According to what Shoma-nii \Nsaid, it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ティナ）\Nあっ お兄さん いらっしゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.49,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome, Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このホテル 住めるように\Nキレイにしておきましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.74,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,I've cleaned up this hotel, \Nso it'd be suitable for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 住むっつっても\N数日間 借りるだけだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:24.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Er, but we're only going to be \Nstaying here for a few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも どうせなら\Nキレイなほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:28.63,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,Still, would it not make you \Nhappier if the place were clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うれしいじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.50,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Who knew
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:34.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）まさか 真夏に\N暖炉をたくはめになるとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.72,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,we'd be lighting the fireplace \Nin the middle of summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:38.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,舞い上がったモノリスの灰が\N太陽を隠してるせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Because of the ashes from the Monolith \Nrising up and hiding the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと３日は寒いらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,they say it'll be cold for the next three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉樹）飯の用意ができたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.74,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,Food's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うまいな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉樹）ヘッ\Nどうよ 見直しただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.95,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,See? Impressed, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（弓月）\N兄貴は 我が家のシェフなの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.98,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,Bro's the chef in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変態のあんたじゃ\N足元にも及ばないんだからね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.58,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,A pervert like you could never compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:59.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I guess you really can't \Njudge a book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:59.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人は見かけによらないとは\Nこのことだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.62,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランは\Nどうして逃げていったのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.79,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Why did Aldebaran run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\Nウワサ話なら飛び交ってるけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:12.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,There are a lot of rumors going around, \Nbut nobody knows for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際のところは分からねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（弓月）また ガストレアは\N攻めてくるかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.28,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,I wonder if the Gastrea will attack again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:19.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉樹）代替えモノリスの完成まで\Nまだ３日あるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.48,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,Not to mention, there are \Nthree more days until the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.39,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,substitute Monolith is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん ちょっといい？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.26,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, do you have a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:26.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）光の槍に\N手足を切断された患者さんを―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:24.90,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,I observed some patients
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.77,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,who had their arms or legs \Ncut off by the Spear of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,診たんだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らは例外なく\N難聴や視野狭窄(きょうさく)といった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,All of them are experiencing \Ndeafness or loss of sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水銀中毒の兆候が見られるの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:35.11,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,which are symptoms of mercury poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水銀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:36.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Mercury?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.44,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,Onii-san, there's something I'd like to report
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も その件で\N１つ報告したいことがあります
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.12,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,about that matter, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦闘中 シェンフィールドで\N５キロ先に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:46.09,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,During the battle, using Shenfield, \NI located a Gastrea,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:49.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水銀を射出したと思われる\Nガストレアを捕捉しました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:49.50,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,five kilometers away, that I \Nbelieve was shooting out mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:50.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなヤツだった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:50.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What did it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.23,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:56.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シェンフィールドに\N画像を送信する機能はないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.57,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Shenfield doesn't have the \Nability to send images.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ 大きさは かなりありました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.76,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,However, it was rather large.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらく ステージⅣです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.26,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,I would say it was a Stage Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:04.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性）失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.76,Bullet_Main,man,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性）里見リーダー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.66,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,Leader Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我堂団長から\Nお呼びがかかりました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.85,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,Commander Gado sent out a summons for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,至急 仮設本部までお越しください
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.98,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Please report to the temporary \Nheadquarters at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我堂が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.29,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Gado?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.04,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（我堂長政(ながまさ)）かけたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:32.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あんた それ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.33,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:36.32,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I got it when I fought with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:37.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツと一戦 交えたときにな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.09,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You mean Aldebaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ヤツって\Nアルデバランのことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.57,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.26,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,However, it didn't take my leg;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが この足は奪われたのではない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.60,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I let 'im have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くれてやったのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:53.10,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,How was my son, Hidehiko, \Nin his final moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せがれの英彦は\Nどのような最期を遂げた？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,He fought very bravely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立派に戦ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.19,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,I'm the one who had him \Nbecome a civil officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれに民警をやらせたのは私だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.45,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,If I had known this was going to happen, I'd have let him do what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:10.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなことになるなら\N好きな道を歩かせてやるべきだった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:14.52,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Gado, don't you think that the \Nenemy has too much of a lead on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）我堂 今回の敵は―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,統率がとれすぎていると\N思わないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.85,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が言いたい？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,After the JASDF won the earlier battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先の戦いで快勝した自衛隊が―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.97,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,why did they lose so quickly this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ 今回は\Nあんなにあっさりやられたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And when Aldebaran was hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランが傷ついたとき―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:27.26,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,why did the surrounding Gastrea form a wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ 周囲のガストレアが\N壁になったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:30.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The answer is... pheromones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その答えは フェロモンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:33.31,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Are you saying it's releasing pheromones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フェロモンを\N噴出しているというのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.37,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The thing that gathered the \NGastrea around Aldebaran was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:37.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）アルデバランの周りに\Nガストレアを集めたのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.75,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,the aggregation pheromone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“集合フェロモン”だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.89,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It seems Aldebaran is using \Npheromones for various purposes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:41.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらく アルデバランは\Nフェロモンを使い分けて―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.03,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,to keep total control over the pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完璧に群れを統率してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.26,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That being the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:48.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとすれば アルデバランを倒せば\N群れは崩壊する
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.87,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,if we defeat Aldebaran, \Nthe pack will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（長政）うむ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:54.33,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,That was a very helpful insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大変 参考になる意見だったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:59.34,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,But I will let you in on some information \Nthat you're not aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:13:00.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では 私も君が知らない情報を\N１つ提供しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.29,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,There is no way to defeat Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランを倒す方法はない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.47,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Aldebaran is immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツは不死身だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:13.70,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,My Varanium blade split its head open
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:14.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のバラニウムの剣は\Nヤツの頭部を断ち割り
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.50,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,and pierced through upon reversal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,返す刃(やいば)で貫いた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:19.29,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,I am sure I dealt damage \Nto its brain and heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:20.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに 脳と心臓に\Nダメージを与えた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.07,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,However, it didn't fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし ヤツは倒れず
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:27.45,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,In the next instant, although slowly, \Nit began to regenerate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:28.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の瞬間 ゆっくりとだが\N傷の再生を始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.07,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:29.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.80,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,And that's not the only trump card they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（長政）しかも\N切り札は それだけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.25,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,The Gastrea with the Spear of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光の槍を持つガストレア
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:40.80,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,It's been identified to be as \Ngreat a threat as Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツは アルデバランと並ぶ脅威と\N認定された
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.96,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Codename: Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コードネームは“プレヤデス”だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Pleiades...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プレヤデス
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.97,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,We cannot win simply by defeating Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（長政）\Nアルデバランを倒すだけでは―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々は勝利できない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:54.48,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Even if we try to defeat the king, \Nthe queen will stand in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:55.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キングを倒そうとしても\N必ず クイーンが立ちはだかる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:59.73,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,In order to win this game, \Neliminating the queen is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:14:00.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このゲームにおいて\Nクイーンの排除は勝利の絶対条件だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:05.99,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Because of that, we must make \Na very difficult decision today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:06.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのうえで 我々は今日\Nつらい決断を下さなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.36,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Leader Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見リーダー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.34,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,In the midst of maneuvers, \Nyou and your adjuvant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:14.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君と君のアジュバントは\N作戦行動中に英彦の陣を離れ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.18,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,strayed from Hidehiko's camp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.91,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,and acted on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単独行動をした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.20,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,That was to eliminate \Nthe enemy's detachment—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは 敵の別動隊を\Nたたくために…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That doesn't change the fact \Nthat you disobeyed orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（長政）命令違反は命令違反だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.83,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Your actions were equal to fleeing \Nin the presence of the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:26.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君たちの行いは\N敵前逃亡に等しく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.09,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,causing a potentially lethal \Ndisturbance in the civil officer ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他の民警に 致命的な動揺を与えた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:32.35,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,You must pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのツケは 払わなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.11,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Leader Satomi, I hereby disband your adjuvant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:36.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見リーダー\N君のアジュバントを解体し
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:37.85,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,and sentence you to capital punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君を極刑に処する！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.60,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:40.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ふざけるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:41.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（剣を抜く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:52.20,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,Leader Satomi, are you \Nprepared to die once again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見リーダー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は もう一度\N死んでみる覚悟はあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.96,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,I believe that if we can defeat Pleiades,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は プレヤデスを倒せば―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:59.85,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,we can find a hole in the wall \Nwe are currently up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:15:01.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この閉塞(へいそく)した状況を\N打開する糸口になると思っている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.38,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:08.47,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,I want you to infiltrate enemy \Nterritory and destroy Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君には 敵地に単独で潜入し\Nプレヤデスを撃滅してほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.11,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You've shown your true colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）本性を現しやがったな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.38,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,You cannot decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君に拒否権はないのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:19.23,Bullet_Main,gado,0,0,0,,In return, I promise your \Nadjuvant will not be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その代わり\N君のアジュバントの罪は―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:20.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問わないことを約束する
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.60,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You conniving old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タヌキじじいが…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（寝息）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまん 延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.61,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Satomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）どこに行くの？ 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,To the bathroom. \NAre you going to follow me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレだよ\Nついてくんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.32,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,With all that luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな荷物 持って？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.97,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I can bring whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を持ってこうが 俺の勝手だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.53,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,So the punishment wasn't just the \Ndisbanding of the adjuvant, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:56.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,処分は アジュバントの\N解散だけじゃなかったのね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.78,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,But by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど １人でなんて\N死にに行くようなものよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.54,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,That's the same as going off to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Someone has to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:04.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かが責任を\N取らなきゃなんないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:12.74,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこに？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.74,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:18.23,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,There's nowhere left to run in the Tokyo Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:19.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）もう 東京エリアに\N逃げ場所なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,If we don't stop it here, we'll die, \Nno matter where we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで食い止めなきゃ\Nどこに逃げても死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:24.25,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's the one thing we have to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけは 避けなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:27.35,Bullet_Main,reen,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kisara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう 木更さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.37,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,You really are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:36.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントに おバカなんだから…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.60,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:47.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（オオカミの遠ぼえ）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:48.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:58.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… うっ うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:24.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:27.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（オオカミのうなり声）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケルベロスの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.90,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I guess this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ… くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:04.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子(ひるこ)影胤(かげたね)）フフフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:16.21,Bullet_Main,hiru,0,0,0,,Well, fancy meeting you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）\Nこんな所で出会うとは 奇遇だね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.40,Bullet_Main,hiru,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,So you were alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:23.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きていたのか 蛭子影胤！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Hiruko Kagetane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:27.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.92,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Would you kindly put your gun down already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ\N銃を下ろしてくれんかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:31.92,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,断る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:38.80,Bullet_Main,hiru,0,0,0,,Have you already forgotten who it was \Nthat gave you bandages and antibiotics?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:37.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）包帯や抗生物質を\N提供しているのは誰なのか―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう忘れたのかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.93,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And you guys haven't forgotten \Nwhat you've done, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）てめえらこそ―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分がしたことを\N忘れたんじゃねえだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして ここにいる？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:48.06,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Are you involved in that \Ngeezer's schemes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:48.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また じじいの悪だくみに\N加担してんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.95,Bullet_Main,hiru,0,0,0,,I have no comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）ノーコメントだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.56,Bullet_Main,kohi,0,0,0,,Where's Enju?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子小比奈(こひな)）延珠は？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.93,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Did she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,She's alive. We're moving separately for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きてるよ\N別行動中だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:00.05,Bullet_Main,kohi,0,0,0,,Oh, good! Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.46,Bullet_Main,kohi,0,0,0,,I want to see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:06.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会いたいな 斬りたいな\N会いたいな 斬りたいな…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:02.90,Bullet_Main,kohi,0,0,0,,I want to cut her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.33,Bullet_Main,kohi,0,0,0,,I want to see her... I want to cut her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.74,Bullet_Main,kohi,0,0,0,,{\a6}I want to see her... I want to cut her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:09.40,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, one could ask \Nwhat it is you're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:10.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）里見くん\N君こそ なぜ こんな所に？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm here to defeat Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プレヤデスを倒すためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.07,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Pleiades?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）プレヤデス？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.25,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It's a Gastrea that shoots out mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水銀を打ち出すガストレアだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.51,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I did see something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）ああ いたね そんなのが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.76,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I was watching the battle yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:22.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日の戦いなら\N見物させてもらったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見物だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why didn't you participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして 戦いに参加しない？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.47,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,What, exactly, waits \Nfor me after this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）\N戦って その先に何がある？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.98,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:30.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平和だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.48,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I've never wished for such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フッ\N一度として 望んだことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You truly are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は壊れている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:41.24,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Have you ever even considered me normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:42.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）今日の今日まで\N私がまともだとでも？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:47.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why do you wear a mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:48.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 どうして仮面をかぶってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フッ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.67,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Would you like to see my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の素顔を見たいかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）いや
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.27,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,That is the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:20:00.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）正解だ\N見たら きっと後悔する
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.30,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You would assuredly regret seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Are you scarred or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）傷でもあんのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:03.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.35,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,The thing under this mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この仮面の下にあるのはね―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:08.14,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,is your own face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の顔だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.77,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.67,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,We possess powers that are beyond humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:15.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）我々は 人をして\N人を超えた力を持っている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:18.73,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,When faced with senseless violence, \Nyou must have thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:19.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君も理不尽な暴力にさらされたとき\N思ったはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:25.31,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,"I have enough power inside me \Nto turn you all into ground meat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の中には お前らを\N簡単にひき肉にできるほどの―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力があるんだぞ と…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.80,Bullet_Main,kagee,0,0,0,,I've been carrying that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は それを実行してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.92,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,That's why you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 君は 私を憎悪するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.76,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You envy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は 私が羨ましい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:36.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.74,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,However, Satomi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）だがね 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:42.31,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Just as you feel about me, I, too, envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:43.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君と同じように\N私も君を羨望しているのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.80,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Living so comfortably in \Nyour world of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:46.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光の世界で\Nぬくぬくと生きている君が―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.16,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I can't help but despise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪わしてくてたまらない！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:52.08,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Come with me, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私と共に来い 友よ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.06,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I shall teach you pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:55.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君に快楽を教えてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:21:00.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I will never mistake how I use my powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:01.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 力の使い方を\N間違えたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.76,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I shall make a prediction, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,予言しよう 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.20,Bullet_Main,kagee,0,0,0,,You will definitely come to this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は 必ず こちらに来る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.96,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっとだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:19.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鳥のさえずり）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.04,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Did they already leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 行ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:33.99,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,A river...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,川か…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.60,Bullet_Main,kagee,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）こんな所にいたのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.61,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,There's something I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君に伝え忘れたことがあった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:44.86,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,We happened to bump into this \NGastrea named Pleiades yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちは 昨日―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プレヤデスとかいうガストレアに\N遭遇した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:45.86,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこで!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.37,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Follow the river upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）そこの川に沿って\N上流に向かえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:52.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:53.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして 俺にそのことを教える？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:56.15,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Well, if I must give a reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:59.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）さて 強いて言うなら\N君が気に入っているからかね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.53,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,it might be because I happen to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）フンッ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:04.88,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:05.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんのつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.06,0:22:09.01,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You just happen to be \Ngoing the same way we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:09.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）私たちの進行方向に\N君がいるだけだが？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:12.10,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）勝手にしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.89,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,And that's precisely what we shall do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）そうさせてもらおう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:25.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:29.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:39.69,Bullet_Next_Ep_Title,title,0,0,0,,#12 Crisis Point
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:32.59,Bullet_Main,hiruko,0,0,0,,This is the world that you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:34.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）これは 君の望んだ世界だ\N君が始末をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.56,Bullet_Main,hiruko,0,0,0,,You must make amends with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.68,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,{\a6}Please, Satomi-kun. Lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:37.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん お願い\N私たちを導いて！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:39.25,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The final battle will be at \Nthe Flames of Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:40.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\N最終決戦の場所は“回帰の炎”だ
